							<h5>Professional Athletes Foundation</h5>
							<p>The Professional Athletes Foundation (PAF) provides financial support to any professional or amateur football player or his immediate family in times of financial crisis. PAF is governed by an elected board of directors that oversee all aspects of the funding process.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.yourpaf.com/about/#.VuBxPvkrK70" title="https://www.yourpaf.com/about/#.VuBxPvkrK70">https://www.yourpaf.com/about/#.VuBxPvkrK70</a> </p>
